  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to telepathy-mission-control</title>

    <para><application>Telepathy-Mission-Control</application> is an account manager
    and channel dispatcher for the Telepathy framework, allowing user interfaces
    and other clients to share connections to real-time communication services
    without conflicting.</para>

    &lfs70_built;

